q000160.options: Underground & Overhead Head Service Lines;Danger of electrocution from cables above and below ground. Stump grinder in contact with Gas, Power, Water.;Service plans needed and checked before work. Treat all lines as if they are live. Get Local Power Authority approval to work within vicinity of power lines - have them disconnected if necessary. Do not fall trees within 2 tree lengths of power lines. All other work not to be done within 4 meters of power lines - that is 4 metres from nearest part of person or vehicle to nearest live line(Minimum Approach Distance MAD) No work to be done alone near power lines. Safety observer to monitor MAD during work and warn of encroachment. Use insulator poles working around service lines.;
